001package apprepo;
002
003public class Application {
004    private String name;
005    private String description;
006    private String organization;
007    private String platforms;
008    private String[] links;
009    private String price;
010    
011    // Getters and Setters
012    // Name
013    public String getName() {
014        return name;
015    }
016    public void setName(String name) {
017        this.name = name;
018    }
019    
020    // Description
021    public String getDescription() {
022        return description;
023    }
024    public void setDescription(String description) {
025        this.description = description;
026    }
027    
028    // Organization
029    public String getOrganization() {
030        return organization;
031    }
032    public void setOrganization(String organization) {
033        this.organization = organization;
034    }
035    
036    // Platforms
037    public String getPlatforms() {
038        return platforms;
039    }
040    public void setPlatforms(String platforms) {
041        this.platforms = platforms;
042    }
043    
044    // Links
045    public String[] getLinks() {
046        return links;
047    }
048    public void setLinks(String[] links) {
049        this.links = links;
050    }
051    
052    // Price
053    public String getPrice() {
054        return price;
055    }
056    public void setPrice(String price) {
057        this.price = price;
058    }
059}
